{
  "name": "Portfolio Orchestrator - Weekly Review",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 12 * * 5"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "weekly-trigger",
      "name": "Friday 12 PM Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [
        0,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Hardcoded business list (replace getMany which doesn't work for file resource)\nreturn [{ json: { name: 'bayflow', path: 'memory-bank/businesses/bayflow' } }];"
      },
      "id": "list-businesses",
      "name": "List All Businesses",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        220,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const businesses = $input.all();\nconst results = [];\nfor (const biz of businesses) {\n  if (biz.json.name === '_template') continue;\n  results.push({\n    json: {\n      businessId: biz.json.name,\n      businessPath: `memory-bank/businesses/${biz.json.name}`\n    }\n  });\n}\nreturn results;"
      },
      "id": "filter-businesses",
      "name": "Filter Active Businesses",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        440,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "get",
        "owner": "ShalinPatel670",
        "repository": "sluice-orchestration",
        "filePath": "={{ $json.businessPath }}/state.md",
        "resource": "file"
      },
      "id": "read-state",
      "name": "Read State",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.github",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        660,
        -50
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "get",
        "owner": "ShalinPatel670",
        "repository": "sluice-orchestration",
        "filePath": "={{ $json.businessPath }}/strategy.md",
        "resource": "file"
      },
      "id": "read-strategy",
      "name": "Read Strategy",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.github",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        660,
        50
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const state = $('Read State').first().json.content || '';\nconst strategy = $('Read Strategy').first().json.content || '';\nconst businessId = $('Filter Active Businesses').first().json.businessId;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    businessId,\n    prompt: `Today is ${new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0]}. You are the Portfolio Orchestrator for The Forge (Forge Technologies).\n\nYou have cross-portfolio intelligence responsibilities. You read all CEO Agent state files and the Knowledge Graph.\n\nHere is the current portfolio data:\n\n## Business: ${businessId}\n### State\n${state}\n\n### Strategy\n${strategy}\n\nPerform your weekly portfolio review:\n\n1. **Revenue Ceiling Enforcement:** Can each business plausibly reach $100K MRR? If ceiling is $15-30K, flag it (still valuable, but no breakout investment).\n\n2. **Distribution Channel Intelligence:** Which keywords are converting? Which content formats drive signups? Identify cross-portfolio patterns.\n\n3. **Breakout Detection:** Any business showing >30% MoM growth? Flag immediately for budget increase.\n\n4. **Kill/Sell Assessment:** Any business with no revenue after 60 days? Any plateaued at $5-30K MRR (sell candidate on Acquire.com at 3-4x annual)?\n\n5. **Content Reuse:** Can winning content strategies from one business be adapted for others in related verticals?\n\n6. **UGC Graduation:** Any business at $5K+ MRR still running 100% AI content? Flag for UGC transition.\n\n7. **Token Budget Audit:** Are AI costs per business reasonable for the stage? Any businesses hitting token caps without results (kill signal)?\n\nOutput your report in markdown with clear action items for each business.`\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "id": "build-prompt",
      "name": "Build Orchestrator Prompt",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        880,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "={{ $json.prompt }}"
      },
      "id": "llm-chain",
      "name": "Orchestrator LLM Chain",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm",
      "typeVersion": 1.4,
      "position": [
        1100,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "claude-opus-4-20250514",
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.3,
          "maxTokens": 3000
        }
      },
      "id": "opus-model",
      "name": "Opus Model",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatAnthropic",
      "typeVersion": 1.3,
      "position": [
        1100,
        220
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "create",
        "owner": "ShalinPatel670",
        "repository": "sluice-orchestration",
        "filePath": "memory-bank/system/orchestrator-review-{{ $now.format('yyyy-MM-dd') }}.md",
        "fileContent": "={{ $json.text }}",
        "commitMessage": "Portfolio Orchestrator weekly review - {{ $now.format('yyyy-MM-dd') }}",
        "resource": "file"
      },
      "id": "write-report",
      "name": "Write Orchestrator Report",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.github",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1320,
        0
      ]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Friday 12 PM Trigger": {
